snippet: In her new album, “Ultraviolence,” Lana Del Rey sets herself further outside whatever passes for current pop mainstream.
abstract: Songwriter Lana Del Rey, on her latest album Ultraviolence, looks to eliminate notion that she is only chasing hits; album delves deeper into her trademark blend of retro sophistication and unending candor, further setting her outside whatever passes for current pop mainstream success.
lead_paragraph: In her new album, “Ultraviolence,” Lana Del Rey sets herself further outside whatever passes for current pop mainstream.

headline.seo: Lana Del Rey Still Stirs Things Up With ‘Ultraviolence’
headline.main: Finding Her Future Looking to the Past
headline.print_headline: Finding Her Future Looking to the Past
